d Angel Investor','Explored the \'Career in Stock Market and Finance\' workshop, which covered stock market basics, career opportunities, and personal finance management tips.','Participants Gained foundational knowledge of the stock market, including its basics and potential career pathways, while also receiving valuable insights on personal finance management during the workshop.','95');
